<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٢٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5093">أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2821">شَيْبَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6882">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3745">أَبِي سَلَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«قَضَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِالْعُمْرَى، أَنَّهَا لِمَنْ وُهِبَتْ لَهُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>